This place that I patronised is just a small canteen that sell mostly indian food, namely, L2 canteen. I was there together with a few of my colleagues in the afternoon, to have our lunch. It mainly caters to indian/bangladesh contract workers and others too. The prices there are quite reasonable. I had a plate of rice with chopped curry mutton,(quite a generous portion) a piece of fried fish and vegetables. It costs me $6.00.
It's wonderfull location to staying here's the environment is very good.
Everything is well prepared but the canteen food here is expen
